Package gamemechanics

Class BoardSpace

java.lang.Object
gamemechanics.BoardSpace
Direct Known Subclasses:
Barrier, Menu, Path
public class BoardSpace extends Object
This class is responsible for setting up the skeleton and framework of the actual board. The class handles the imaging and coordinates of the object to be drawn on the board.
